Melissa Howard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melissa_Howard 0 Melissa Beck (born Melissa Howard) is a reality show personality, and comedian, known for her time as a cast member on the 2000 reality television series The Real World: New Orleans, and the 2002–2005 prank show Girls Behaving Badly.
